                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>Paez</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Pto Cabello</placeName>, <date>1<hi rend=\"sup\">st</hi>\n                    June 1854</date></p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Isaac Leeser Esqr</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dear sir,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Your very esteemed favour <date>12<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi></date>\n                ulto. duly came to hand<lb/> and having been prevented of this pleasure ere this, I\n                hasten<lb/> now to assure you that I have done every thing in my power<lb/> to\n                circulate your books, but I have but little hope of succeeding<lb/> as there are\n                very few of our persuasion in this part of the world;<lb/> very few or none of them\n                understand the <sic>hebrew</sic>, and few the<lb/>\n                <sic>english</sic> language; however, I must in justice acknowledge<lb/> that those\n                that were able to read some of your works, ma<lb/>-nifested a desire to possess\n                them, and have asked me to re<lb/>-quest you for a catalogue. A few copies of your\n                little books<lb/> for young people will be well received.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><persName>Mr David Lobo</persName> of this place requested me to\n                inquire<lb/> about a small amount that he is indebted to you for<lb/> works sent out\n                to him, which he wishes to deliver into my<lb/> hands to be transmitted to you</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">With many wishes for the happy return of the<lb/> season, I\n                remain,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">Dear sir,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">Yours respectfully</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(11)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">A Myerston</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>I trust that by this time you have received from <persName>Messrs.<lb/> Dovale &amp;\n                    Co.</persName> the amt. of the last books.</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p31j97t97/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
